#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Endurance
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000250F"
msgid "He doesn't know anything, he's too old. Doesn't have that *fire* in him anymore. But no worries, *we* will carry on. *Semper fidelis*, kingsman!"
msgstr ""
"Да он же ничего не знает, слишком стар. Былой *огонь* в нем давно угас. Но не переживай, *мы* продолжим службу. *Semper fidelis*, рыцарь!"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000253B"
msgid "The old soldier nods. \"Even after the Revolution, after the Beachhead, there was a chance. Had we just stayed true to our *values*...\""
msgstr ""
"Старый солдат кивает. «Даже после Революции, после плацдарма все равно оставался шанс. Сохрани мы верность своим *ценностям*...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000258C"
msgid "\"'This time'?!\" He's becoming visibly annoyed. \"What happened to the first time? Did you make a mistake? Did you *fuck up*? Everyone did!\""
msgstr ""
"«„В этот раз“? — Он явно раздражен. — А в первый раз что мешало? Ошибся? *Облажался*?! Все облажались!»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002764"
msgid "\"So... Is there anything else you want from these gentlemen, or can we get back to it?\""
msgstr ""
"«Так что?.. Вам нужно еще что-нибудь от этих джентльменов? Или мы можем вернуться к расследованию?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000279A"
msgid "\"Alright, you got your laugh, ruined my concentration and our game... Anything else you want, or can we start a new one?\""
msgstr ""
"«Ну ладно, посмеялись и хватит. Ты и так уже испортил и мой настрой, и игру в целом... Тебе еще что-нибудь нужно? Или мы все-таки можем начать новую партию?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Alternate1/0x010000510000279A"
msgid "\"Alright, you got your laugh, ruined my concentration and our game... *again*. Anything else you want to ruin, or can we start a new one?\"\n"
msgstr ""
"«Ну ладно, посмеялись и хватит. Ты и так уже испортил и мой настрой, и игру в целом... *Опять*. Хочешь еще что-нибудь испортить? Или мы все-таки можем начать новую партию?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027B3"
msgid "\"No, I didn't mean it like that.\""
msgstr ""
"«Нет, я не это имел в виду»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024E5"
msgid "\"Oh, you're in for a treat, officer. Seeing the playful side of old René is about as rare as a red rainbow.\""
msgstr ""
"«О! Красную радугу и то чаще увидишь, чем старика Рене в таком шутливом настроении. Тебе понравится!»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002541"
msgid "\"I'm not sure, to be honest. Just going with the flow.\""
msgstr ""
"«Честно говоря, не уверен. Я просто плыву по течению»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002593"
msgid "\"And there are no second chances. We don't deserve them! You can't just go back and restart -- that would make everything *MEANINGLESS*!\" A shadow of pain comes over his face."
msgstr ""
"«Второго шанса не будет, мы его не заслужили! Ты не можешь вернуться назад и начать все заново — тогда всё станет *БЕССМЫСЛЕННЫМ*!» По его лицу пробегает тень боли."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025D9"
msgid "\"You know, it's not actually that bad.\""
msgstr ""
"«Ну, на самом деле все не так уж плохо»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002681"
msgid "*Something* about this topic was very personal to him, but the moment has passed."
msgstr ""
"Этот вопрос связан для него с чем-то очень *личным*, но момент упущен."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026B9"
msgid "Regret about what?"
msgstr ""
"Сожаление? О чем?"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "tooltip1/0x01000051000026B9"
msgid "Bonded over flamethrowers."
msgstr ""
"Сошлись на любви к огнеметам."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "tooltip2/0x01000051000026B9"
msgid "Heard about Jeanne-Marie."
msgstr ""
"Слышал о Жанне-Мари."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026BF"
msgid "No, this is going too far. I should respect his privacy!"
msgstr ""
"Это и так зашло слишком далеко. Нужно уважать его личные границы!"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000248D"
msgid "He thinks you're playing a joke on him."
msgstr ""
"Он думает, ты решил над ним подшутить."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024C9"
msgid "\"Forensic techniques are your forte, not mine, officer.\" Something stiffens in the man. He shakes his head. \"Find another fool, I will not be part of your... joke.\""
msgstr ""
"«Методы криминалистики — твоя вотчина, не моя. — Что-то в нем напрягается. Старик качает головой. — Найди другого дурака, а я не хочу принимать участия в твоих... шутках»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000943D"
msgid "\"Him?\""
msgstr ""
"«О нем?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Composure
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000262D"
msgid "His eyes seem to be pleading with you."
msgstr ""
"Он бросает на тебя умоляющий взгляд."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000263B"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""
"Что же это?"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002641"
msgid "Even thinking about it is invading his privacy. Better let it go."
msgstr ""
"Одна лишь мысль об этом уже нарушает его личные границы. Лучше не трогать."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000273F"
msgid "\"Where?!\" His head drops between his shoulders he snaps around with surprising speed."
msgstr ""
"«Где?!» Он пригибает голову и осматривается с проворством, достойным удивления."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000275D"
msgid "\"*Meaningless* is what I think this line of questioning is. Call me a sceptic, but I don't think time travel is going to solve our murder case.\""
msgstr ""
"«*Бессмыслица* — вот что я думаю об этой линии сбора показаний. Можете считать меня скептиком, но я не верю, что путешествия во времени помогут нам раскрыть убийство»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002669"
msgid "\"Look, I just want to turn back time. Can either of you help me or not?\""
msgstr ""
"«Послушайте, я лишь хочу обернуть время вспять. Кто-нибудь из вас может помочь мне в этом?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002726"
msgid "\"Kim?\""
msgstr ""
"«Ким?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000272C"
msgid "\"War.\""
msgstr ""
"«Война»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Savoir Faire
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002746"
msgid "Retired or not, there's still a trained killer in there."
msgstr ""
"В отставке или нет — боец остается бойцом."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027B9"
msgid "\"Did I say that out loud?\""
msgstr ""
"«Я что, сказал это вслух?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Volition
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027C9"
msgid "You know what you meant, but taking this kind of scolding does *not* feel good."
msgstr ""
"Ты знаешь, что имел в виду. Но получать такой нагоняй все равно *неприятно*."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000282A"
msgid "\"Yes.\" The lieutenant turns to look at you as well. \"What else, officer?\""
msgstr ""
"«Да. — Лейтенант тоже поворачивается к тебе. — В чем же еще, офицер?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Half Light
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002552"
msgid "You could *definitely* clear it with a flamethrower."
msgstr ""
"Ну уж *огнемет*-то с этим точно справился бы."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Rhetoric
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025B2"
msgid "There's so much bitterness in his voice it barely even registers as sarcasm."
msgstr ""
"В его голосе так много горечи, что сарказм распознается с трудом."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025DF"
msgid "Just nod."
msgstr ""
"Просто кивнуть."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Volition
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002634"
msgid "He would sooner die than let it surface."
msgstr ""
"Но он скорее умрет, чем даст ему вырваться."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002754"
msgid "No... not gun. Something repressed and painful. Too late. The moment has passed."
msgstr ""
"Нет... дело не в оружии. Тут какое-то болезненное вытеснение. Поздно, момент упущен."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100009426"
msgid "\"Anything else you want or can we get back to our game?\""
msgstr ""
"«Тебе еще что-нибудь нужно, или мы можем вернуться к игре?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000251E"
msgid "\"It's always about love, isn't it?\""
msgstr ""
"«Любовь всегда виновата, так ведь?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025D3"
msgid "\"It *is* an ugly world...\""
msgstr ""
"«Мир *действительно* уродлив...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Endurance
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026A1"
msgid "The carabineer is too old and feeble to be useful. But you will carry on. *Movere tempore*, kingsman. For the tenacious no road is impassable."
msgstr ""
"Карабинер слишком стар и немощен: он бесполезен. Но ты продолжишь службу. *Movere tempore*, рыцарь. Для стойких духом безвыходных ситуаций не бывает."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026A9"
msgid "\"*Imbécile, un putain d'imbécile*...\" The old veteran clutches his chest and tries to steady his breathing."
msgstr ""
"«*Imbécile, un putain d'imbécile*...» Старый ветеран хватается за грудь и пытается восстановить дыхание."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Volition
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026F5"
msgid "Willed back into the darkest unexplored depths of his mind -- never meant to be shared, seen or confronted."
msgstr ""
"Его затягивает обратно в самые темные и неисследованные пучины разума, о которых нельзя говорить, которыми нельзя делиться, которым нельзя противостоять."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024D0"
msgid "\"I thought you were a busy man, officer. Or at least you should be, so I won't comment on this... eccentricity. Now what?\""
msgstr ""
"«А я-то считал тебя занятым человеком, господин полицейский. Так что я, пожалуй, оставлю свои мысли при себе. Еще что-нибудь?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024D7"
msgid "\"*Bon sang*, son. You must have a loose screw up there or something.\" He taps on his temple. \"Sounds like you really mean it.\""
msgstr ""
"«*Bon sang*, сынок. У тебя, наверное, шарики за ролики заехали. — Он постукивает себя по виску. — Ты говоришь это будто на полном серьезе»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000254B"
msgid "\"It happened slowly, like a seedling growing into a tree. Tiny incremental steps. Imperceptible till the thicket was so thick you couldn't clear it with a flamethrower...\""
msgstr ""
"«Это произошло постепенно — как будто семя проросло и стало деревом. Медленно, шаг за шагом. Незаметно превратилось в такую густую чащу, с которой даже огнемет не справится...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002585"
msgid "\"The 'right track'? This *is* the right track! The only track.\" He gets visibly annoyed. \"This is the world we shaped, a reflection of what we are: cowardly, ugly, and numb.\""
msgstr ""
"«„В нужное русло“? Это *и есть* нужное русло! Единственное из возможных. — Он явно раздражен. — Это мир, который мы сотворили, отражение нас самих — трусливый, уродливый, оцепенелый»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002738"
msgid "\"I'm not gonna say anything.\""
msgstr ""
"«Я лучше промолчу»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027D7"
msgid "\"Enough yacking!\" the carabineer cuts Gaston off mid-sentence. \"We have a game to finish, so let's get back to it, unless there's something else?\""
msgstr ""
"«Хорош трепаться! — карабинер обрывает Гастона на полуслове. — Нас ждет игра, вернемся к ней. Если, конечно, у господина полицейского нет к нам других вопросов»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024B5"
msgid "\"No, I literally need to go back in time. For Revachol.\""
msgstr ""
"«Нет. Мне нужно отправиться в прошлое. В буквальном смысле. Ради Ревашоля»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Alternate1/0x01000051000024B5"
msgid "\"I'm not kidding. This is for Revachol. I need to return to the past.\""
msgstr ""
"«Я не шучу. Это ради Ревашоля. Мне нужно вернуться в прошлое»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000274D"
msgid "\"Goddamnit, son...\" He turns back to you, frowning. \"As an officer of the law you should know better than... damn it! Are we done here?\""
msgstr ""
"«Черт побери, сынок... — Нахмурившись, он снова поворачивается к тебе. — Ты же представитель правопорядка, нельзя же быть таким... дери тебя за ногу! Надеюсь, это всё?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002774"
msgid "\"What the hell are we talking about here, officer?\" He rubs the back of his head. \"Look, we just want to play our game, so unless there's something else...\""
msgstr ""
"«Почему мы вообще говорим об этом, черт побери? — Он почесывает затылок. — Слушай, мы просто хотим продолжить игру, так что, если у тебя всё...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000944B"
msgid "There's tenderness in the carabineer's look. Tenderness that's curdled into pain or something darker."
msgstr ""
"В глазах карабинера отражается нежность. Нежность, свернувшаяся комьями боли или чего-то еще более мрачного."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024DF"
msgid "\"Alright, I will entertain this... *fantasy*, if you tell me, what interest does an RCM officer have in... 'time travel'?\""
msgstr ""
"«Ну ладно, я подыграю твоему... *воображению*, если ты мне скажешь, зачем РГМ нужны... „путешествия во времени“»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002663"
msgid "\"*Everyone* deserves a second chance.\""
msgstr ""
"«*Кто угодно* заслуживает второй шанс»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026D8"
msgid "Him."
msgstr ""
"О нем."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000276D"
msgid "\"W-war?\" The word seems to derail his train of thought. \"I mean yes. Yes... It changes men, changes lives and uh...\""
msgstr ""
"«В-война? — Кажется, это слово сбило его с мысли. — Ну, то есть, да. Конечно... Она меняет людей, меняет жизни и э-э-э...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002783"
msgid "Shouldn't have brought him into this. He doesn't know pain like you do."
msgstr ""
"Не нужно было его в это втягивать. Он знаком с болью не так близко, как ты."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Esprit de Corps
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002815"
msgid "Damn it, not this again..."
msgstr ""
"Боже, только не это..."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Esprit de Corps
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000247C"
msgid "What are you up to now?"
msgstr ""
"Что ты там еще задумал?"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002485"
msgid "\"What?!\" The old soldier scowls at you, unamused."
msgstr ""
"«Что?!» Старый солдат, нахмурившись, серьезно смотрит на тебя."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Encyclopedia
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024ED"
msgid "Not actually *that* rare. It's just that red, or monochrome, rainbows usually occur at sunrise or sunset, when blue and green wavelengths are scattered before reaching water droplets. Fewer eyes to see them then."
msgstr ""
"Ну на самом деле это *не настолько* редкое явление. Все дело в том, что красная, или одноцветная, радуга обычно появляется на закате или на восходе, когда цвета синего и зеленого спектра рассеиваются, прежде чем достигнуть капелек воды. Не самое многолюдное время."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025C0"
msgid "The lieutenant clears his throat. \"I think we're done here unless you have questions *not* relating to 'time travel' for the gentlemen?\""
msgstr ""
"Лейтенант прочищает горло. «Полагаю, вопрос закрыт. Если у вас, конечно, нет к этим джентльменам других вопросов, *не связанных* с „путешествиями во времени“»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002679"
msgid "*Something* about this topic was very personal to him, but the moment has passed."
msgstr ""
"Этот вопрос связан для него с чем-то очень *личным*, но момент упущен."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002696"
msgid "\"But don't worry, I'm sure there's something else old René or I can assist you with.\""
msgstr ""
"«Но не расстраивайся, я уверен, мы со старым Рене наверняка поможем в чем-нибудь другом»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026E5"
msgid "You catch the old carabineer's gaze slowly leaving his opponent's wrinkled face as his dark eyes meet yours -- whatever turmoil raged in him a moment ago is quelled for now."
msgstr ""
"Старый карабинер медленно переводит взгляд с морщинистого лица соперника на тебя. Ты смотришь в его темные глаза. Беспокойство, терзавшее его всего мгновение назад, угасло."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002720"
msgid "\"Gun!\""
msgstr ""
"«Оружие!»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000277B"
msgid "War isn't tied with regret for him. Nevermind, the moment is gone."
msgstr ""
"Война не связана для него с сожалением. Неважно, момент все равно упущен."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027A5"
msgid "\"That's just *typical*!\" The carabineer looks at you with disgust. \"All you young guys these days. You want to be opinionated, controversial, opposition leaders...\""
msgstr ""
"«Ну *конечно*! — Карабинер смотрит на тебя с отвращением. — Вы, молодежь, совсем не уважаете чужое мнение. Лишь бы поспорить, выразить свое несогласие...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002461"
msgid "\"René... I need to go back in time. Can you help me?\""
msgstr ""
"«Рене... Мне нужно отправиться в прошлое. Поможешь мне?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002534"
msgid "\"Men have lost their way. I want to guide them back. Like a beacon.\""
msgstr ""
"«Человечество заблудилось. Я хочу вернуть его на путь истинный. Стать маяком»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025EB"
msgid "A heavy silence falls over the crater. The man in the checkered suit doesn't know where to look or what to do with his hands. Finally he speaks:"
msgstr ""
"Над воронкой повисает напряженная тишина. Мужчина в клетчатом костюме не знает, куда деть взгляд и что делать с руками. Наконец, он снова заговаривает."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000268F"
msgid "\"Enough, officer,\" the other one says with surprising resoluteness. \"We can't help you. Not with this. Such an *emotional* topic...\""
msgstr ""
"«Достаточно, — на удивление решительно произносит второй старик. — Мы не можем тебе помочь. По крайней мере в этом. В таком *эмоциональном* вопросе...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024A2"
msgid "\"No, I need to go back to a time when *love* was still possible.\""
msgstr ""
"«Нет. Я хочу вернуться в то время, когда *любовь* еще была возможна»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Alternate1/0x01000051000024A2"
msgid "\"I'm dead serious. Can you help me get back to the time when *love* was still possible?\""
msgstr ""
"«Я абсолютно серьезен. Ты поможешь мне вернуться в то время, когда *любовь* еще была возможна?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002560"
msgid "\"I *know* I can get history back on the right track.\""
msgstr ""
"«Я *знаю*, что могу повернуть историю в нужное русло»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025FB"
msgid "Only to break the silence."
msgstr ""
"Лишь бы нарушить молчание."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000256C"
msgid "\"Well, that depends on the flamethrower...\""
msgstr ""
"«Ну, зависит от огнемета...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002575"
msgid "\"It really does, doesn't it?\" The old soldier produces a strange croaking sound -- with laughter-like qualities -- then quickly massages his chest. \"But honestly, why?\""
msgstr ""
"«Зависит, не так ли? — Старый солдат издает странный каркающий звук, отдаленно похожий на смех, и принимается растирать себе грудь. — Но правда, зачем?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026DE"
msgid "You know the answer, don't think -- just say it!"
msgstr ""
"Ты же знаешь ответ. Не думай — скажи."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Conceptualization
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026EE"
msgid "Like the last rays of the evening sun gently kissing the day goodbye, before giving way to unfathomable darkness."
msgstr ""
"Как последние лучи вечернего солнца, которые нежно целуют день на прощание, прежде чем уступить непроглядной тьме."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027C1"
msgid "\"Oh save it.\" He waves you off. \"Men don't have substance anymore, I know that, but seeing such spinelessness in a man bearing an insignia...\""
msgstr ""
"«Ой, хватит, — отмахивается он от тебя. — У людей сейчас и так нет внутреннего стержня. Это мы уже проходили. Но чтобы человек в форме был таким бесхребетным...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000945A"
msgid "Even worse, a love aborted and smothered, stamped beneath his brilliant boot heel."
msgstr ""
"И даже хуже — любовь, уничтоженная, задушенная, растоптанная каблуками его великолепных ботинок."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002626"
msgid "\"Easy, René, take it easy.\" There's genuine concern in his face. \"You're right, absolutely right. What was, *was* and that's it. Isn't that right, officer?\""
msgstr ""
"«Тихо, тихо, Рене. — На его лице отражается неподдельное беспокойство. — Ты прав, совершенно прав. Что было, то *прошло*. Не так ли?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000264D"
msgid "Honour walks and virtue follows. You are truly a Detective-Saint, for you refuse to veer even when *no one* is looking. Bravo!"
msgstr ""
"Честь — истинная добродетель. Такого детектива, как ты, воистину можно назвать святым за то, что не стал увиливать, даже когда *никто* не видит. Браво!"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002672"
msgid "\"*Imbécile, un putain d'imbécile*...\" The old veteran clutches his chest and tries to steady his breathing."
msgstr ""
"«*Imbécile, un putain d'imbécile*...» Старый ветеран хватается за грудь и пытается восстановить дыхание."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027D0"
msgid "\"You must forgive mean old René, officer!\" The other one jumps in. \"He can't stop being himself more than a scorpion can stop being a sco...\""
msgstr ""
"«Прости старого ворчливого Рене, начальник! — встревает в разговор второй старик. — Он такой, какой есть: скорпион не перестанет быть ско...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024BB"
msgid "\"Right, right... A forensic technique. Can you help me or not?\""
msgstr ""
"«Да-да, конечно... Метод в криминалистике. Так ты мне поможешь или нет?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002517"
msgid "\"Love. It's about love.\""
msgstr ""
"«Любовь. Все дело в любви»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025B9"
msgid "\"I can't help you officer,\" he says coldly. \"There are no second chances in life. We don't deserve them. This is the world we shaped -- a reflection of what we are. Wasted, ugly, and numb.\""
msgstr ""
"«Я ничем не могу тебе помочь, — холодно произносит он. — Жизнь не дает второго шанса. Мы его не заслужили. Это мир, который мы сотворили, отражение нас самих — опустошенный, уродливый, оцепенелый»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002603"
msgid "\"Officer, you must forgive Old René. Holding a conversation has always been... problematic with him.\" He flashes you a quick smile. \"Try asking him something else.\""
msgstr ""
"«Прости старого Рене, начальник. Такие беседы всегда вызывали у него... сложности. — Он робко улыбается. — Спроси его лучше о чем-нибудь другом»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002687"
msgid "\"*Imbécile, un putain d'imbécile!*...\" The old veteran clutches his chest and tries to steady his breathing."
msgstr ""
"«*Imbécile, un putain d'imbécile!..*» Старый ветеран хватается за грудь и пытается восстановить дыхание."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026B0"
msgid "\"No, officer.\" He shakes his head meekly. \"We can't help you with that, maybe there's something else we *can* help you with?\""
msgstr ""
"«Нет. — Он робко качает головой. — С этим мы тебе помочь не можем. Но, может, тебе нужна помощь с чем-нибудь *другим*?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000027AC"
msgid "\"But as soon as the talk turns real and there's a smallest amount of friction you're suddenly 'not gonna say anything'. Better to be wrong than a goddamn coward!\""
msgstr ""
"«Но как только разговор становится серьезным, и появляется малейший намек на трения, вы сразу такие „лучше промолчу“. Уж лучше ошибаться, чем быть трусом!»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Reaction Speed
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000284B"
msgid "'Here we go again.'"
msgstr ""
"«Ну вот, опять»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100009454"
msgid "Ex-love, ex-tenderness..."
msgstr ""
"Бывшая любовь, бывшая нежность..."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000259B"
msgid "There's something *substantial* moving in him, trying to get out."
msgstr ""
"Какое-то очень *важное* чувство мечется в нем, пытаясь пробиться наружу."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002647"
msgid "Regret."
msgstr ""
"Сожаление."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Endurance
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002711"
msgid "The carabineer is too old and feeble to be useful. But you will carry on. *Movere tempore*, kingsman. For the tenacious no road is impassable."
msgstr ""
"Карабинер слишком стар и немощен: он бесполезен. Но ты продолжишь службу. *Movere tempore*, рыцарь. Для стойких духом безвыходных ситуаций не бывает."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Composure
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002476"
msgid "His posture tenses."
msgstr ""
"Его тело напрягается."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Gaston Martin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002495"
msgid "\"Now, now...\" His partner raises both hands in a calming gesture. \"I'm sure the officer means it figuratively. Like a forensic technique or something, right?\""
msgstr ""
"«Ну-ну... — Его товарищ поднимает руки, пытаясь успокоить старика. — Уверен, господин полицейский говорит лишь образно, метафорически. Это что-то типа метода в криминалистике или вроде того. Так ведь?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Reaction Speed
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002525"
msgid "Was that a smile on his wrinkled... nevermind, it's gone."
msgstr ""
"Неужели это улыбка на его морщинистом... проехали, ее уже нет."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002840"
msgid "The lieutenant rubs his forehead and mumbles something under his breath."
msgstr ""
"Лейтенант почесывает лоб и что-то бормочет себе под нос."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000053000053B6"
msgid "The old carabineer looks at you with wary expectation."
msgstr ""
"Старый карабинер недоверчиво и выжидательно смотрит на тебя."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002470"
msgid "The lieutenant flashes you a quick side-glance."
msgstr ""
"Лейтенант бросает на тебя косой взгляд."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Rhetoric
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000257C"
msgid "Keep the war-crime jokes coming and you'll end up on his good side."
msgstr ""
"Продолжай свои шуточки на тему военных преступлений, и он придет в хорошее расположение духа."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025AB"
msgid "\"Exactly what history needs.\" He spits on the ground between the two of you. \"More drifters, confused wanderers, weightless men...\""
msgstr ""
"«Именно то, что нужно истории. — Он сплевывает на землю вам под ноги. — Бродяги, бестолковые скитальцы, легкомысленный народ...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000025E5"
msgid "\"Such a downer, I'm not even sure how to respond...\""
msgstr ""
"«Я даже не знаю, как реагировать на такие упаднические настроения...»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Endurance
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002619"
msgid "Don't worry, he doesn't know anything useful, the man's almost expired. No fire in him. But *you* will carry on the flame. *Semper fidelis*, kingsman, anything is possible."
msgstr ""
"Не расстраивайся, он все равно ничего полезного не знает, его срок подходит к концу. Былой огонь угас. *Тебе* предстоит нести это пламя дальше. *Semper fidelis*, рыцарь. Нет ничего невозможного."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002703"
msgid "\"Our lives are unique, and I have neither the means nor the will to help you change that.\" A polite nod. \"But I will gladly assist you with police matters.\""
msgstr ""
"«Жизнь каждого человека уникальна, и у меня нет ни возможностей, ни желания помогать тебе изменить это. — Он вежливо кивает. — Однако я с удовольствием помогу в расследовании»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002732"
msgid "\"Dad?!\""
msgstr ""
"«Папа?!»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000278C"
msgid "No, not that one."
msgstr ""
"Нет, не то."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002793"
msgid "\"Wh...? Oh, I see.\" He takes a step back and nods, jaw clenched tight. \"You're a comedian after all. Funny guy. *Unpredictable*.\""
msgstr ""
"«Что?.. А, понял. — Он отходит на шаг и, стиснув зубы, кивает. — Ты все-таки комик. Юморист. *Невероятно*»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000024C1"
msgid "\"Forget it. Let's move on.\" (Drop it.)"
msgstr ""
"«Забудь. Проехали». (Оставить идею.)"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = René Arnoux
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000252C"
msgid "\"But it's never *only* about love, so what else, officer?\""
msgstr ""
"«Но дело ведь *не только* в любви. Так в чем же еще, господин полицейский?»"

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002566"
msgid "\"I just want a second chance. Gonna do it right this time.\""
msgstr ""
"«Мне нужен второй шанс. В этот раз я сделаю всё как надо»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000510000265D"
msgid "\"Sure, why not?\""
msgstr ""
"«Да, конечно»."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Composure
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000051000026FC"
msgid "A true master of his emotions."
msgstr ""
"Истинный хозяин своих эмоций."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = Inland Empire
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100002709"
msgid "Hopelessly alone behind the unbreakable walls he spent a lifetime erecting. No one will ever know him."
msgstr ""
"Безнадежно одинокий за нерушимыми стенами, которые возводил всю жизнь. Его никто никогда не поймет."

#. Title = PLAZA / RENE TURNING BACK TIME
#. Description = Ask René if he knows a way to turn back time
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = René Arnoux
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005100009444"
msgid "\"Who?\""
msgstr ""
"«О ком?»"
